# hello03

Minimal Node + TypeScript HTTP server that responds with "Hello 03" on GET /.

Prerequisites
- Node.js 18+ recommended

Install

1. Install dependencies:

   npm install

Run (development)

- Run directly with ts-node (no build):

   npm run dev

Build and Start

1. Build:

   npm run build

2. Start:

   npm start

Tests

- Run tests (uses jest + ts-jest):

   npm test

The server listens on PORT environment variable or 3000 by default.


